                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d680">
                <head>No. 678.<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">General <persName type="from">Sickles</persName> to Mr.
                            <persName type="to">Fish</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Madrid</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1873-12-15T16:30:00-00:14">
                            <hi rend="italic">December</hi> 15, 1873—4.30 p.m.</date> (Received 3.20
                        p.m.)</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>President Casteiar called at the legation this afternoon and informed me that the
                    Virginius and survivors had been surrendered to those authorized to receive them
                    on the part of the United States.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>SICKLES.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
